title: It Was ‘Win Now’ vs. ‘Win Later’ at the NFL’s Trade Deadline
description: The Vikings pulled off an in-division trade, the Ravens got some help for the middle of their defense, and the Jaguars made a bet on the future.
dc:creator: Victor Mather
media:description: Tight end T.J. Hockenson doesn’t have to travel far to get to his new team, the Minnesota Vikings, from his old, the Detroit Lions.
